# Achemy Standards

- This project uses Alchemy to deploy to Cloudflare. Always change deployment config through the alchemy config files.
- Source of truth: packages/infra/alchemy.run.ts + Alchemy env for D1/R2/KV/bindings/flags/secrets.
- apps/web/.alchemy/local/wrangler.jsonc is treated as generated for dev / configPath, not where you define production resources.
- Avoid extra deploy wrangler.toml / wrangler.jsonc under apps/\* unless Alchemy can’t model something and you document an exception.
